buffton corp <buff> buys b and d instruments
    fort worth, tex., march 4 - 
buffton corp said it completed the purchase of b and d industruments
inc for two mln dlrs cash and 400,000 shares of common stock. it said
b and d is a private company headquartered in kansas, and had sales of
4,700,000 dlrs in 1986. buffton said the company designs and
manufactures aviation computer display systems and engine
instrumentation. reuter 
